&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">5 different performances during the evening including a tradtional dance on arrival&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">Individually printed menus with the person&#39;s name and company logo if desired</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">Themed tables can be arranged</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">Torch and candlelit surrounds</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">Full Catering and performance teams</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">Venue Hire</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">Mineral water and cold towel</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">24 hours support by our team</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><